<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="box pink-card">
      <h1 class="title">About NailSpot Dublin</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">NailSpot Dublin is a Points of Interest web application that helps users discover and organise nail salon locations in Dublin.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Each POI stores useful details such as salon name, area, address, services, rating, personal notes, and map coordinates.</p>
      <p>The application is useful for women, tourists, students, and anyone who wants to save favourite nail salons around Dublin.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
